content:
Omni-Channel supercharges your queues to route work items to your agents in real time. Agents donâ€™t have to select work items manually from queues because Omni-Channel routes work items to agents automatically and in real time!

To set up Omni-Channel: Customize Application is required. Available in Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

Queues are assigned the priority that you specified in the routing configuration. Reuse existing queues or create at least one queue to integrate with Omni-Channel. Assign each agent to the queue from which they are receiving work items.

In Setup, enter Queues, select Queues, create a queue, and edit it. Look up the routing configuration and add agents to the Selected Users field. Click Save.
